			<h1 class="article-title"><a href="index.html?p=4698">《这样写出好故事》</a></h1>
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span class="item">2019-10-25</span>
												<span class="item">分类：<a href="literature/index.html" rel="category tag">文学</a></span>
				<span class="item post-views">阅读(1285)</span>				<span class="item">评论(0)</span>
